{{obsolete}}

Certain creatures can '''cling''' to the walls of the dungeon, allowing them to pass over otherwise impassable terrain as long as they stay orthogonally adjacent to a wall (they cannot cling to only a corner).

Creatures that can cling to walls:<ref>{{source ref|0.24.0|mon-util.cc|845}}</ref>

{{monsterlink|Giant cockroach}}

{{monsterlink|Dart slug}}

{{monsterlink|Leopard gecko}}

{{monsterlink|Demonic crawler}}

'''[[List of arthropods#Spiders|All spiders]]'''

==History==
*Clinging was removed in [[0.25]].
*Prior to [[0.15]], players could cling using [[Spider Form]] or [[boots of the spider]].
*Wall-clinging was added in [[0.8]].

